    <introduction>
      <para>Error BAT0001: A configuration file must be specified and it must
exist</para>
    </introduction>

    <section>
      <title>Cause</title>
      <content>
        <para>This error occurs if the <codeInline>ConfigurationFile</codeInline>
property on the <codeInline>BuildAssembler</codeInline> build task has not been
set, is set to an empty string, or refers to a file that does not exist.</para>
      </content>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>Solution</title>
      <content>
        <para>Specify a valid file that exists for the
<codeInline>ConfigurationFile</codeInline> property on the
<codeInline>BuildAssembler</codeInline> build task in the project file.</para>
      </content>
    </section>

